  stimulus_text = 'The new CEO announced that she would be implementing  a new policy to encourage employees to use their vacation time,  a change that was designed to boost morale and productivity.  She also explained that  the policy  would  be  phased  in  over the next quarter,  giving  employees  time to adjust to the new guidelines.  She  believes  that  the  policy  will  have  a  positive impact on  employee  well-being,  and  improve  the company’s overall performance.',
